ike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T08:07:07.000Z","msg":"燒山做埋影評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3ec7cb9d8256f4809a11147ffee95f9e5adaa17","tid":1663084,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T08:32:08.000Z","msg":"【香城施政報告2019】群策群力 轉危為機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656908</a><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>政治問題</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 重塑公民身分戶口政策保障國家、香港安全和利益<br />\n- 取消18區區議會、建立地域市政議會<br />\n- 禁止公務人員在任前、任內和任後獲港外榮典<br />\n- 改善高鐵一地兩檢操作方式<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>便民基建</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 興建東鐵、西鐵快速線並完善輕鐵和西鐵聯乘關係<br />\n- 完善機場集體運輸並加強機場、港珠澳大橋協同發展<br />\n- 修正港鐵、巴士可加可減機制<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>醫療、教育方向</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 興建至少四所新區域全科醫院<br />\n- 以減少送院為目標的社區護理服務<br />\n- 重塑教育, 著重知識、技能層次分工<br />\n<br />\n求正評及幫推！"},{"pid":"99fb09d3663dfb75da5b30461381f54e18eea5f7","tid":1663084,"uid":103263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51924481103cdd8aaa9b120a185d2d078b970995","tid":1663084,"uid":21141,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T08:07:07.000Z","msg":"燒山做埋影評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T11:32:48.000Z","msg":"唐伯虎點秋香佢監制架"},{"pid":"3e0d80864938369ea79f0cdc0bc1a11c9a6af3ad","tid":1663084,"uid":137569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51924481103cdd8aaa9b120a185d2d078b970995","tid":1663084,"uid":21141,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T08:07:07.000Z","msg":"燒山做埋影評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T11:47:25.000Z","msg":"佢知名編劇同監製嚟"},{"pid":"4eebc70db1376be513a13e7bed19e3cea709d30a","tid":1663084,"uid":279356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T11:54:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g3rZEXN.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/t